1
00:00:00,330 --> 00:00:01,040
大家好
dà jiā hǎo
Hi everyone!

2
00:00:01,050 --> 00:00:03,640
今天的视频除了记录我的日常工作
jīn tiān de shì pín chú le jì lù wǒ de rì cháng gōng zuò
Today's video, besides documenting my daily work,

3
00:00:04,530 --> 00:00:07,280
更重要的是我有一个特别的挑战
gèng zhòng yào de shì wǒ yǒu yí gè tè bié de tiǎo zhàn
more importantly, I have a special challenge.

4
00:00:07,650 --> 00:00:11,465
我会用iPad Pro做完所有的工作
wǒ huì yòng iPad Pro zuò wán suǒ yǒu de gōng zuò
I'll use the iPad Pro to do all my work,

5
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:14,990
看看它到底能不能代替电脑
kàn kàn tā dào dǐ néng bù néng dài tì diàn nǎo
to see whether it can actually replace a computer.

6
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:19,230
我一般的工作内容包括写稿子
wǒ yì bān de gōng zuò nèi róng bāo kuò xiě gǎo zi
My usual work includes writing scripts,

7
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:20,390
拍视频
pāi shì pín
filming videos,

8
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:21,630
剪视频
jiǎn shì pín
editing videos,

9
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,870
发帖子
fā tiē zi
posting on social media,

10
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:24,270
上网课等等
shàng wǎng kè děng děng
teaching online classes, and so on.

11
00:00:24,930 --> 00:00:27,600
我们就来看看我能不能完成这个挑战
wǒ men jiù lái kàn kàn wǒ néng bù néng wán chéng zhè ge tiǎo zhàn
Let's see if I can complete this challenge.

12
00:00:28,010 --> 00:00:31,620
一般早上的第一件事就是
yì bān zǎo shàng de dì yī jiàn shì jiù shì
Usually the first thing in the morning is

13
00:00:31,630 --> 00:00:32,340
撸狗
lū gǒu
petting the dog.

14
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:35,780
每天早上起床后他就会在沙发上
měi tiān zǎo shàng qǐ chuáng hòu tā jiù huì zài shā fā shàng
Every morning after I get up, he'll be on the couch

15
00:00:35,790 --> 00:00:37,060
翻肚子撒娇
fān dǔ zi sā jiāo
rolling onto his back, being cute and clingy,

16
00:00:37,070 --> 00:00:37,570
要我摸摸
yào wǒ mō mō
wanting me to pet him.

17
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:47,150
撸完狗以后我会马上喝水
lū wán gǒu yǐ hòu wǒ huì mǎ shàng hē shuǐ
After petting the dog, I'll drink water right away.

18
00:00:47,370 --> 00:00:50,560
我现在用的是40盎司的杯子
wǒ xiàn zài yòng de shì 40 àng sī de bēi zi
I'm currently using a 40-ounce cup.

19
00:00:50,570 --> 00:00:52,640
每天至少要喝两杯
měi tiān zhì shǎo yào hē liǎng bēi
I need to drink at least two cups a day.

20
00:00:52,650 --> 00:00:54,280
虽然休斯顿回暖了
suī rán xiū sī dùn huí nuǎn le
Even though Houston has warmed up,

21
00:00:54,290 --> 00:00:56,840
早上起来我还是觉得非常冷
zǎo shàng qǐ lái wǒ hái shì jué de fēi cháng lěng
I still feel very cold when I wake up in the morning.

22
00:00:57,630 --> 00:00:58,300
然后就要给毛孩子们早餐
rán hòu jiù yào gěi máo hái zi men zǎo cān
Then I need to give the furry kids their breakfast.

23
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:02,620
这是非常重要的日程
zhè shì fēi cháng zhòng yào de rì chéng
This is a very important part of the schedule.

24
00:01:11,540 --> 00:01:27,690
还是很困
hái shì hěn kùn
Still very sleepy.

25
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:30,820
所以我赶紧做了一杯咖啡提神
suǒ yǐ wǒ gǎn jǐn zuò le yī bēi kā fēi tí shén
So I quickly made a cup of coffee to wake myself up.

26
00:01:31,030 --> 00:01:32,880
我们家的咖啡机很简单
wǒ men jiā de kā fēi jī hěn jiǎn dān
Our coffee machine is very simple.

27
00:01:33,150 --> 00:01:34,990
我也不是什么咖啡专家
wǒ yě bú shì shén me kā fēi zhuān jiā
And I'm not really a coffee expert either.

28
00:01:40,210 --> 00:01:43,160
我喜欢喝浓缩加燕麦奶
wǒ xǐ huān hē nóng suō jiā yàn mài nǎi
I like espresso with oat milk.

29
00:01:43,170 --> 00:01:44,920
我会打发奶泡
wǒ huì dǎ fā nǎi pào
I'll froth some milk.

30
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:49,420
随便弄一杯浓缩
suí biàn nòng yī bēi nóng suō
Just make an espresso.

31
00:01:53,230 --> 00:02:06,830
最后加上我的巧克力酱
zuì hòu jiā shàng wǒ de qiǎo kè lì jiàng
Finally add my chocolate sauce.

32
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,020
我最近很迷甜口的咖啡
wǒ zuì jìn hěn mí tián kǒu de kā fēi
Lately I've been really into sweet coffee.

33
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:17,560
接下来我就会开门放Crockett去院子里上厕所
jiē xià lái wǒ jiù huì kāi mén fàng Crockett qù yuàn zi lǐ shàng cè suǒ
Next I'll open the door and let Crockett go to the yard to use the bathroom,

34
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:19,800
让它跑一跑
ràng tā pǎo yī pǎo
and let him run around a bit.

35
00:02:19,810 --> 00:02:22,560
它真的是一只欢乐的小狗
tā zhēn de shì yī zhī huān lè de xiǎo gǒu
He's really such a happy little dog.

36
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:25,500
这个就是我早上的日程
zhè ge jiù shì wǒ zǎo shàng de rì chéng
This is my morning routine.

37
00:02:25,830 --> 00:02:27,380
我刚洗漱了一下
wǒ gāng xǐ shù le yī xià
I just freshened up a bit,

38
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,500
然后把头发拉直了
rán hòu bǎ tóu fā lā zhí le
and straightened my hair.

39
00:02:29,510 --> 00:02:31,150
我做了早餐
wǒ zuò le zǎo cān
I made breakfast:

40
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,830
两个菜包
liǎng gè cài bāo
two vegetable buns,

41
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:37,260
两个豆沙包都在Weee上买的
liǎng gè dòu shā bāo dōu zài Weee shàng mǎi de
and two red bean buns, both bought on Weee.

42
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:40,410
今天这个视频主要就是想记录
jīn tiān zhè ge shì pín zhǔ yào jiù shì xiǎng jì lù
Today's video is mainly meant to document

43
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:44,050
一下我今天在家工作一天的日常
yī xià wǒ jīn tiān zài jiā gōng zuò yī tiān de rì cháng
my daily routine of working from home today.

44
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,390
最近我买了一个新的iPad
zuì jìn wǒ mǎi le yí gè xīn de iPad
I recently bought a new iPad,

45
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,390
是m4的iPad PRO
shì m4 de iPad PRO
the M4 iPad Pro.

46
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:52,330
然后我第一次买了蜂窝数据版的
rán hòu wǒ dì yī cì mǎi le fēng wō shù jù bǎn de
And for the first time I bought the cellular version,

47
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,850
就是带移动数据的
jiù shì dài yí dòng shù jù de
meaning the one with mobile data.

48
00:02:53,860 --> 00:02:56,810
然后昨天我也把它弄好了
rán hòu zuó tiān wǒ yě bǎ tā nòng hǎo le
I got it set up yesterday too.

49
00:02:57,130 --> 00:03:00,260
根据我现在的手机再多加一个
gēn jù wǒ xiàn zài de shǒu jī zài duō jiā yí gè
Based on my current phone plan, I added another line—

50
00:03:00,270 --> 00:03:04,230
平板的流量套餐是每个月多15 美元
píng bǎn de liú liàng tào cān shì měi gè yuè duō 15 měi yuán
the tablet's data plan is an extra $15 a month.

51
00:03:05,270 --> 00:03:07,820
然后是无限制的流量
rán hòu shì wú xiàn zhì de liú liàng
And it's unlimited data,

52
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:10,380
5g的流量我觉得还挺划算的
5g de liú liàng wǒ jué de hái tǐng huá suàn de
5G data, which I think is a pretty good deal.

53
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:13,980
是我在所有的选择中看到是最便宜的
shì wǒ zài suǒ yǒu de xuǎn zé zhōng kàn dào shì zuì pián yi de
It's the cheapest option I saw among all the choices.

54
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:17,210
所以昨天我已经弄好了
suǒ yǐ zuó tiān wǒ yǐ jīng nòng hǎo le
So I already got it set up yesterday.

55
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:19,810
因为我住的这个地方有的时候会突然停电
yīn wèi wǒ zhù de zhè ge dì fāng yǒu de shí hòu huì tū rán tíng diàn
Because where I live, the power sometimes suddenly goes out.

56
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:22,330
去年就遇到过好几次
qù nián jiù yù dào guò hǎo jǐ cì
I ran into this several times last year,

57
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:24,490
然后在上课的途中突然停电
rán hòu zài shàng kè de tú zhōng tū rán tíng diàn
with the power suddenly going out in the middle of class,

58
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:25,570
就很尴尬
jiù hěn gān gà
which is really awkward—

59
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:27,050
要用我的手机来上课
yào yòng wǒ de shǒu jī lái shàng kè
having to use my phone to teach instead.

60
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:30,000
所以我决定还是把我的iPad 加上移动数据
suǒ yǐ wǒ jué dìng hái shì bǎ wǒ de iPad jiā shàng yí dòng shù jù
So I decided to add mobile data to my iPad after all.

61
00:03:30,970 --> 00:03:32,160
这样的话如果停电了
zhè yàng de huà rú guǒ tíng diàn le
That way, if the power goes out,

62
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:34,320
我也可以继续用iPad来上课
wǒ yě kě yǐ jì xù yòng iPad lái shàng kè
I can still keep teaching using the iPad.

63
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:38,300
今天主要工作的内容就是要做语法视频
jīn tiān zhǔ yào gōng zuò de nèi róng jiù shì yào zuò yǔ fǎ shì pín
Today's main work is to make a grammar video.

64
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:41,030
我已经想好主题了
wǒ yǐ jīng xiǎng hǎo zhǔ tí le
I've already thought of the topic,

65
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,710
但是我还没写好那个稿子和PDF
dàn shì wǒ hái méi xiě hǎo nà ge gǎo zi hé PDF
but I haven't written the script and PDF yet.

66
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,790
所以第一我要先把PDF写好
suǒ yǐ dì yī wǒ yào xiān bǎ PDF xiě hǎo
So first I need to finish writing the PDF,

67
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,830
然后要录这个视频
rán hòu yào lù zhè ge shì pín
then record the video,

68
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:51,710
然后剩下的时间我会去剪这个视频
rán hòu shèng xià de shí jiān wǒ huì qù jiǎn zhè ge shì pín
then use the remaining time to edit it.

69
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:54,990
下午4点我还有一节课
xià wǔ 4 diǎn wǒ hái yǒu yī jié kè
I have a class at 4pm,

70
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:58,390
所以在这节课以前我能剪多少
suǒ yǐ zài zhè jié kè yǐ qián wǒ néng jiǎn duō shǎo
so however much I can edit before that class...

71
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,390
明天的课比较多
míng tiān de kè bǐ jiào duō
Tomorrow I have more classes,

72
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,670
所以可能没有太多的时间剪视频
suǒ yǐ kě néng méi yǒu tài duō de shí jiān jiǎn shì pín
so I might not have much time to edit the video.

73
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:05,710
今天希望能够尽量的把大部分的剪出来
jīn tiān xī wàng néng gòu jǐn liàng de bǎ dà bù fèn de jiǎn chū lái
Today I hope to edit as much of it as possible.

74
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:10,630
然后我也会尝试所有的工作都在我的iPad上完成
rán hòu wǒ yě huì cháng shì suǒ yǒu de gōng zuò dōu zài wǒ de iPad shàng wán chéng
I'll also try to do all my work on my iPad.

75
00:04:12,230 --> 00:04:14,110
目前我已经试了两天了
mù qián wǒ yǐ jīng shì le liǎng tiān le
So far I've tried it for two days,

76
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,190
基本上95%的工作我都可以用我的iPad来完成
jī běn shàng 95% de gōng zuò wǒ dōu kě yǐ yòng wǒ de iPad lái wán chéng
and basically 95% of my work I can do on my iPad.

77
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,510
今天这个视频就是一个记录
jīn tiān zhè ge shì pín jiù shì yí gè jì lù
Today's video is just a record of that.

78
00:04:19,520 --> 00:04:21,960
所以我现在来吃个早餐
suǒ yǐ wǒ xiàn zài lái chī gè zǎo cān
So now I'll go have breakfast,

79
00:04:21,970 --> 00:04:24,190
然后我们就可以开始准备工作
rán hòu wǒ men jiù kě yǐ kāi shǐ zhǔn bèi gōng zuò
and then we can start getting ready for work.

80
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:26,700
我不知道有没有人跟我一样
wǒ bù zhī dào yǒu méi yǒu rén gēn wǒ yī yàng
I don't know if anyone else is like me—

81
00:04:26,710 --> 00:04:28,820
我不喜欢吃肉包子
wǒ bù xǐ huān chī ròu bāo zi
I don't like eating meat buns.

82
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:31,100
就包子的话我吃不了肉包子
jiù bāo zi de huà wǒ chī bù liǎo ròu bāo zi
When it comes to buns, I can't eat meat buns.

83
00:04:31,380 --> 00:04:33,690
我特别喜欢吃素馅儿的包子
wǒ tè bié xǐ huān chī sù xiàn ér de bāo zi
I especially love buns with vegetarian filling.

84
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:38,590
这个是香菇青菜包我觉得特别香
zhè ge shì xiāng gū qīng cài bāo wǒ jué de tè bié xiāng
This is a mushroom and vegetable bun, I think it smells amazing.

85
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:46,080
皮也很软味的包子真的不错
pí yě hěn ruǎn wèi de bāo zi zhēn de bù cuò
The skin is soft too, this bun is really good.

86
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:51,810
这个小的是红豆包
zhè ge xiǎo de shì hóng dòu bāo
This small one is a red bean bun,

87
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:52,690
特别小
tè bié xiǎo
it's really small.

88
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:54,200
这是红豆
zhè shì hóng dòu
This is red bean,

89
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:55,440
这个是菜包
zhè ge shì cài bāo
and this is a vegetable bun.

90
00:04:56,250 --> 00:04:58,120
红豆包打开来
hóng dòu bāo dǎ kāi lái
Opening up the red bean bun,

91
00:04:58,130 --> 00:05:01,760
它是那种比较细腻的豆沙馅儿
tā shì nà zhǒng bǐ jiào xì nì de dòu shā xiàn ér
it has a smooth, fine red bean paste filling.

92
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:05,210
其实我喜欢吃那种比较粗一点的
qí shí wǒ xǐ huān chī nà zhǒng bǐ jiào cū yì diǎn de
Actually I like the kind that's a bit coarser,

93
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:07,370
可以尝得到豆沙皮的那种豆沙馅儿
kě yǐ cháng dé dào dòu shā pí de nà zhǒng dòu shā xiàn ér
where you can taste bits of bean skin in the paste,

94
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,670
但是没有买到
dàn shì méi yǒu mǎi dào
but I couldn't find that kind to buy.

95
00:05:09,670 --> 00:05:19,730
我的咖啡在这儿还是好困呢
wǒ de kā fēi zài zhè ér hái shì hǎo kùn ne
My coffee's right here, and I'm still so sleepy.

96
00:05:19,980 --> 00:05:21,050
桌面的布置
zhuō miàn de bù zhì
As for the desk setup,

97
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:23,490
因为我要尝试只用iPad来完成工作
yīn wèi wǒ yào cháng shì zhǐ yòng iPad lái wán chéng gōng zuò
since I'm trying to do all my work using only the iPad,

98
00:05:24,140 --> 00:05:25,890
所以电脑我就没有放在桌子上了
suǒ yǐ diàn nǎo wǒ jiù méi yǒu fàng zài zhuō zi shàng le
I didn't put my computer on the desk.

99
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:27,290
我只放了我的iPad
wǒ zhǐ fàng le wǒ de iPad
I only put out my iPad,

100
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:30,130
我的耳机还有笔
wǒ de ěr jī hái yǒu bǐ
my headphones, and a pen.

101
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:31,170
我还有一个鼠标
wǒ hái yǒu yí gè shǔ biāo
I also have a mouse—

102
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:33,430
就是鼠标它可以连连接三个不同的设备
jiù shì shǔ biāo tā kě yǐ lián lián jiē sān gè bù tóng de shè bèi
it can connect to three different devices.

103
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,790
现在把它连到了iPad上面
xiàn zài bǎ tā lián dào le iPad shàng miàn
Right now I've connected it to the iPad,

104
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:39,350
所以如果我用这个触控板累了的话
suǒ yǐ rú guǒ wǒ yòng zhè ge chù kòng bǎn lèi le de huà
so if I get tired of using the trackpad,

105
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,270
我可以用鼠标来操作
wǒ kě yǐ yòng shǔ biāo lái cāo zuò
I can use the mouse instead.

106
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:44,190
我们现在就来开始写语法视频的稿子
wǒ men xiàn zài jiù lái kāi shǐ xiě yǔ fǎ shì pín de gǎo zi
Now let's start writing the script for the grammar video.

107
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:46,960
这个就是我的iPad屏幕
zhè ge jiù shì wǒ de iPad píng mù
This is my iPad screen.

108
00:05:46,970 --> 00:05:49,040
我其实是有4个不同的屏幕的
wǒ qí shí shì yǒu 4 gè bù tóng de píng mù de
I actually have 4 different screens set up.

109
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:51,000
这里可以看到这个是home
zhè lǐ kě yǐ kàn dào zhè ge shì home
