00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,270
它就会全屏
tā jiù huì quán píng
and it goes fullscreen.

225
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:35,390
然后我点这里它就会往下走
rán hòu wǒ diǎn zhè lǐ tā jiù huì wǎng xià zǒu
Then when I tap here, it moves forward,

226
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,550
然后同时我也可以用我的笔在
rán hòu tóng shí wǒ yě kě yǐ yòng wǒ de bǐ zài
and at the same time I can also use my pen

227
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,710
上面写画画
shàng miàn xiě huà huà
to write and draw on it,

228
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,030
学生都能看得到
xué shēng dōu néng kàn dé dào
and the students can see it all.

229
00:11:40,030 --> 00:11:43,650
右边是我们上课共用的一个google doc 的文档
yòu biān shì wǒ men shàng kè gòng yòng de yí gè google doc de wén dàng
On the right is a shared Google Doc we use during class,

230
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:45,460
做笔记
zuò bǐ jì
for taking notes.

231
00:11:45,460 --> 00:11:48,810
学生写作业都会在这个上面来写
xué shēng xiě zuò yè dū huì zài zhè ge shàng miàn lái xiě
Students do their homework writing on this too.

232
00:11:48,820 --> 00:11:50,290
我在用Zoom的时候
wǒ zài yòng Zoom de shí hòu
When I'm using Zoom,

233
00:11:50,300 --> 00:11:52,770
学生看到的就是我整个屏幕的这个样子
xué shēng kàn dào de jiù shì wǒ zhěng gè píng mù de zhè ge yàng zi
this is what students see—my whole screen.

234
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:56,750
我觉得这个方法还是挺流畅的
wǒ jué de zhè ge fāng fǎ hái shì tǐng liú chàng de
I think this method is pretty smooth.

235
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:59,950
有的时候上课需要播放一些课文的音频
yǒu de shí hòu shàng kè xū yào bō fàng yī xiē kè wén de yīn pín
Sometimes during class I need to play audio from the textbook,

236
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,510
我就会把 files app也打开
wǒ jiù huì bǎ files app yě dǎ kāi
so I'll also open the Files app,

237
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,610
但是我会把它隐藏在旁边
dàn shì wǒ huì bǎ tā yǐn cáng zài páng biān
but I'll keep it hidden off to the side.

238
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:09,450
所以如果我需要播放音频的时候
suǒ yǐ rú guǒ wǒ xū yào bō fàng yīn pín de shí hòu
So when I need to play audio,

239
00:12:09,460 --> 00:12:11,170
比如说听课文回答问题
bǐ rú shuō tīng kè wén huí dá wèn tí
like listening to a passage to answer questions,

240
00:12:11,180 --> 00:12:16,890
我就会直接左滑就可以滑出files
wǒ jiù huì zhí jiē zuǒ huá jiù kě yǐ huá chū files
I'll just swipe left and Files will slide out,

241
00:12:18,860 --> 00:12:20,260
然后就可以点击播放了
rán hòu jiù kě yǐ diǎn jī bō fàng le
then I can tap play.

242
00:12:20,260 --> 00:12:20,680
对
duì
Yeah.

243
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:23,150
现在已经5点多了
xiàn zài yǐ jīng 5 diǎn duō le
It's already past 5 now.

244
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:24,830
我要去做晚饭了
wǒ yào qù zuò wǎn fàn le
I need to go make dinner.

245
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,830
做完晚饭不知道会不会继续剪一下视频
zuò wán wǎn fàn bù zhī dào huì bú huì jì xù jiǎn yī xià shì pín
I don't know if I'll keep editing the video after dinner,

246
00:12:28,290 --> 00:12:29,960
因为我觉得我大概只剪了一半左右
yīn wèi wǒ jué de wǒ dà gài zhǐ jiǎn le yí bàn zuǒ yòu
since I think I've only edited about half of it.

247
00:12:30,690 --> 00:12:32,280
然后明天的课有很多
rán hòu míng tiān de kè yǒu hěn duō
And I have a lot of classes tomorrow,

248
00:12:32,290 --> 00:12:34,240
我不一定有时间能剪完
wǒ bù yí dìng yǒu shí jiān néng jiǎn wán
so I might not have time to finish editing.

249
00:12:34,250 --> 00:12:35,360
我们吃完晚饭再看
wǒ men chī wán wǎn fàn zài kàn
We'll see after dinner.

250
00:12:35,370 --> 00:12:37,120
这就是今天的视频
zhè jiù shì jīn tiān de shì pín
That's today's video.

251
00:12:37,130 --> 00:12:39,080
感谢大家收看
gǎn xiè dà jiā shōu kàn
Thanks everyone for watching,

252
00:12:39,090 --> 00:12:42,400
跟我一起用iPad度过一天
gēn wǒ yì qǐ yòng iPad dù guò yī tiān
and for spending a day with me using the iPad.

253
00:12:42,410 --> 00:12:43,080
拜拜
bài bài
Bye-bye.
